{
  "stem": "18258.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Incidentally, further down in a number-- I think it was number 14 or something like that-- was also a house in which a former army member of the Austrian army by the name Adolf Hitler had-- had temporary lodgings.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes, it was Adolf Hitler had lived in Stumpergasse in Vienna for a short time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- no, that was not while I was a child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was maybe a little bit later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It might have been in the late teens or early 20s.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I remember it was-- became quite well known.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The name-- the-- the company was known as Siegfried Schneider-- Siegfried was my dad's first name.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Siegfried Schneider [NON-ENGLISH] [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Shirt or underwear manufacturing company.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was on the front of our business, going over the area of three windows, the complete front of the store, plus the sewing room which had windows to the street.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While he was with the dragoons, he also had gotten training in communication, and he was a communication telegraph specialist.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had learned operating the Morse machines.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as specialist as such, although he was already 40 years old, he was called immediately when the First World War started because they needed the communication.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he then served also until the end of the war in 1918 in the infantry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was wounded twice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "During that time, he occasionally came back to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have a very nice picture where he's seen in his uniform with his sergeants walking, the three stars on his collar, and surrounded by some other people of his outfit.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] During the war-- at the beginning, it wasn't too bad.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But by 1916, I remember, we started occasionally being hungry.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
